{"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/07-20-the-inside-shows-through","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016"]]},"topicSectionsStyle":"detailedGrid","kind":"article","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/brunow\/07-20-the-inside-shows-through"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Brunow"}],"color":{"standardColorIdentifier":"purple"},"title":"The Inside Shows Through","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"2017.01.20","name":"Brunow"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"date: 2016-07-20T22:22:32-05:00"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A good façade must be thick enough to mask what lies beneath it. It adds bulk and in my mind unnecessary weight. A bad façade barely hides what is below it and causes a feeling of disease in the minds of those who see it as they try to tie the inside and outside together.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Not using a façade only works if what is inside is what you want to show the world.","type":"text"}]}]}],"references":{"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/2016":{"type":"topic","kind":"article","role":"collectionGroup","abstract":[],"title":"2016","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016","url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/2016"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","title":"Brunow","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"David Brunow, known as Brunow [ˈbɹunoʊ] to the folks he works with, is a human living on Earth. You might have something in common with him — if you think it is ridiculous that he is talking about himself in the first person here, so does he.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","url":"\/documentation\/brunow"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/Archive":{"type":"topic","kind":"article","role":"collectionGroup","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"All posts"}],"title":"Archive","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/archive"}}}